Thence S 15º 00′ E., 1,050 meters to Corner 21;

Thence S 32º 00′ E., 600 meters to Corner 22;

Thence S 12º 00′ E., 1,000 meters to Corner 23;

Thence S 03º 00′ W., 550 meters to Corner 24;

Thence S 10º 00′ E., 875 meters to Corner 25;

Thence S 51º 00′ W., 500 meters to Corner 1, the

point of beginning containing an area of ONE THOUSAND SEVEN HUNDRED EIGHTY SIX (1,786.0) HECTARES more or less.

The administration, control and management of the reservation shall be under the Department of Natural Resources, thru the Bureau of Forest Development.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

DONE in the City of Manila, this 10th day of June, in the year of Our Lord, nineteen hundred and eighty-seven.

(SGD) CORAZON C. AQUINO President of the Philippines

By the President: (SGD) JOKER P. ARROYO Executive Secretary

